这里可以用 ES 6 的模板字符串来代替 `+` 的串联地狱，让整段代码更加容易懂些

## 推荐
```
var a = 5;
var b = 10;
console.log(`Fifteen is ${a} and\nnot ${b}.`);
// "Fifteen is 5 and
// not 10."
```

## 不推荐
```
var a = 5;
var b = 10;
console.log("Fifteen is " + a + " and\nnot " + b + ".");
```

